     C           KEYMA1    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           M1KENO
     C                     KFLD           M1KENA
     C                     MOVEL'0'       GET11   1
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    WKSTAT  2
     C                     Z-ADD0         WKSNDT  80
